Currently, it's work on ubuntu 14.0 as follows,
  1. sudo apt-get install texlive-xetex.
     ref. http://blog.sciencenet.cn/blog-725052-826695.html
  2. Change Makefile as in this folder.
     ref http://www.openfoundry.org/tw/foss-programs/9018-sphinx-restructuredtext-
  3. Change conf.py.linux as in this folder.
     ref http://codeing-niwyclin.logdown.com/posts/196526-sphinx-chinese-pdf

On iMac, 
  1. cp conf.py.imac conf.py as in this folder.
     ref http://blog.chenming.info/blog/2013/03/02/using-sphinx-to-generate-chinese-pdf/
